YOLO - "You Live Only Once". aka "sudo rm -rf /"
This tool was created to fill important gap within our lifes. Because sometimes you just want to say "FTS!" and go for a holiday. But your code, github, codepen, facebook, twitter, instagram... etc not giving you the chance. So here you the tool to show your computer middle finger.

Issues:
May cause some pain, such as:
 * Normall life.
 * Long rest.
 * Kids.
 * Family.
 * Decrease in size of beard.

Compatibility:
*nix systems.

